title: The Lucky One (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor Swift wrote The Lucky One and even though it has parallels to her own life, she had someone else's story in mind. Who is rumored to be the inspiration behind this song? There are lots of theories, including one from our very own Ana!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us. Just let us know!
